# The kernel and its SIMH test programs now build out-of-source into kernel/build/,
# covered by `build/' above.

# The user libraries and their SIMH/b6sim test programs now build out-of-source into
# build/lib/, covered by `build/' above -- including the generated syscall stubs, the
# linked test images, and the .out/.tmp scratch each run leaves behind.

# Scratch drum and disk images that kernel/test/mbtest.ini and mdtest.ini create with
# `attach -n'.  The disk images are ~8 Mb each and there are three of them.
*.drum
*.disk
